column2: Please Note: I have updated the structure of our User Stories. Many of the fields now autopopulate values. Please don't make structural changes unless you know what you are doing. I'll continue to make this form more user firendly as I have time. As a seperate note, I have made all of the tests hidden for the moment, feel free to unhide as needed to work on them. I have also changed our ordering to more closely group items together, and put them in at least a possible general order that we could attack them. We will have to discuss as a group which to keep, which to modify, and what to prioritize. Have a good weekend. Mitchell Kane
